room_title: Escape room "Prohibition" by Escape Room Yuma in Yuma
room_description: This inconspicuous bar is hiding in the dark alleys of the city. Only regular customers know the way, including you, close friends of Skinny Tony, The owner of this establishment. But here comes a sudden police raid and you only have 60 minutes to clean up the evidence at the bar and sneak through the back door. Dare you find a way to escape in time.
